snippet.title: Helicopter Search and Rescue Simulator Review - Worth a Buy?
snippet.description:
Become an emergency pilot and test your skills to their limits, as you sit in the cockpit of an emergency helicopter, across more than 40 challenging missions. Choose from 8 models of 'copter, each varying in size, ability and specs. - But is it Worth a Buy?
